OL,4,CBernard Hill
OL,6,FActors from Lord of the Rings pay
OL,7,Ftribute to Bernard Hill, who has died
OL,8,Fat the age of 79.
OL,10,FThe cast of the Lord of the Rings have
OL,11,Fpaid tribute to the late who they
OL,12,Fstarred alongside in two of the Oscar-
OL,13,Fwinning films.
OL,15,FThe Manchester-born actor died
OL,16,Fsuddenly at the age of 79 on Sunday
OL,17,Fmorning. He was due to appear at but
OL,18,Fpulled out of the event on Friday
OL,19,Fevening.
