OL,3,CLord of the Rings cast pay tribute to
OL,4,CBernard Hill
OL,6,FThe event organisers said they were
OL,7,F"heartbroken" and that they would be
OL,8,Fthinking of his family at this "very
OL,9,Fsad time".
OL,11,FElijah Wood, Billy Boyd, Dominic
OL,12,FMonaghan and Sean Astin, who play four
OL,13,FHobbits in the trilogy, have paid
OL,14,Ftribute to Bernard at the event where
OL,15,Fthey were headlining.
OL,17,FSean, who plays Samwise Gamgee, began
OL,18,Fby saying: "We love him. He was
OL,19,Fintrepid, he was funny he gruff, he
OL,20,Fwas irascible, he was beautiful."
