OL,3,CLord of the Rings cast pay tribute to
OL,4,CBernard Hill
OL,6,FEchoing Sean's words, Billy Boyd, who
OL,7,Fplays Pippin, said: "We were watching
OL,8,Fthe movies and I said to Dom, I don't
OL,9,Fthink anyone spoke Tolkien's words as
OL,10,Fgreat as Bernard did.
OL,12,F"He would break my heart. He will be
OL,13,Fsolely missed."
OL,15,FBernard played Captain Edward Smith in
OL,16,Fthe Oscar-winning 1997 epic romance
OL,17,FTitanic, which starred Leonardo
OL,18,FDiCaprio and Kate Winslet.
