OL,3,CLord of the Rings cast pay tribute to
OL,4,CBernard Hill
OL,6,FHe also portrayed Theoden, King of
OL,7,FRohan, in The trilogy directed by Sir
OL,8,FPeter Jackson.
OL,10,FHill joined the cast for the second
OL,11,Ffilm in the trilogy, 2002's The Two
OL,12,FTowers, which won two Academy Awards
OL,13,Ffor best sound editing and best visual
OL,14,Feffects.
OL,16,FLord of the Rings cosplayers pay
OL,17,Ftribute to Bernard Hill at Liverpool
OL,18,FComic Con, the event he was due to
OL,19,Fattend as a guest.
