OL,3,CLord of the Rings cast pay tribute to
OL,4,CBernard Hill
OL,6,FHe returned to the franchise for
OL,7,F2003's The Return Of The King, which
OL,8,Fpicked up 11 Oscars, including best
OL,9,Fpicture and best director for Sir
OL,10,FPeter.
OL,12,FHill first made a name for himself as
OL,13,FYosser Hughes in Alan Bleasdale's Boys
OL,14,FFrom The Blackstuff, which aired in
OL,15,F1982 about five unemployed men.
OL,17,FThe role earned him a Bafta TV
OL,18,Fnomination in 1983, the same year the
OL,19,Fshow picked up the Bafta for best
OL,20,Fdrama series.
