OL,6,FPaying tribute, Comic Con Liverpool
OL,7,Fsaid: "We're heartbroken to hear the
OL,8,Fnews of Bernard Hill's passing. A
OL,9,Fgreat loss.
OL,11,F"Thinking of his family at this very
OL,12,Fsad time, and wishing them a lot of
OL,13,Fstrength."
